This package helps C programmers by displaying information about the arguments of C functions. It uses a C function database, which you can create from man pages or from your own sources

You can get this package from:

* http://vengeance.et.tudelft.nl/~smoke/pub/emacs/c-mode-addons-0.1.tar.gz

You can also get a ready C functions database from 

* http://vengeance.et.tudelft.nl/~smoke/pub/emacs/c_synopsis_list.tar.gz

: There is also an ElDoc you might be interested. --ZajcevEvgeny

